Package ro.ubb.truckers.repository.mapper.file

Interface FileMapper<T>

Type Parameters:
T - representing the type of entity that is mapped.
All Known Implementing Classes:
CompanyFileMapper, DeliveryFileMapper, GarageFileMapper, TruckFileMapper, UserCompanyFileMapper, UserFileMapper
public interface FileMapper<T>
A file mapper helps with interpreting the read data from the files and with formatting the entity for writing data into files.
